{"tid":1054114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧琼：適時啟動基本法23條諮詢及立法","createTime":"2019-03-09T15:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T16:49:03.000Z","uid":7828,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b543d3ef538eb9715ef9c8e2d92204c39e5592c4","tid":1054114,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T15:15:25.000Z","msg":"正在北京的全國政協委員、民建聯主席李慧琼指，目前有港獨勢力，趁23條未立法搗亂，認為是適當時候啟動諮詢。<br />\n<br />\n李慧琼：「確實過去因為沒有廿三條，有港獨勢力趁機搗亂，希望我們大家理性去對待及處理廿三條。我認為是適當時候，需要啟動諮詢程序及立法工作。」<br />\n<br />\n李慧琼之後主動向本台解釋，她的意思是在適當時候才啟動23條立法工作，而非指目前要啟動立法。"},{"pid":"0850d418dbb3a9c3459ffd46ac5b5fe9021c6ca2","tid":1054114,"uid":52595,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T15:26:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd8c58742eb73a81cc0f8bacba81eebb08961fb7","tid":1054114,"uid":205844,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T15:32:44.000Z","msg":"搞搞搞，搞左民生先啦<br />\n有樓住方你立唔到法咩<br />\n用屎忽諗野?"},{"pid":"317761c1ea59e55b69d23ec5aaa0b0263b36ffbc","tid":1054114,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T15:39:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40e7beaf4d63ee45c980a7f0a8dd15bdf123022d","tid":1054114,"uid":18955,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"太慢啦<br />\n港府應該宣布<br />\n由於港獨份子不受控<br />\n進入緊急狀態<br />\n全國性法律在香港實行<br />\n即時拉柒晒班港獨份子<br />\n<br />\n咁就快靚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f76cbeeaa183c476264145959d8d47dcc3d648","tid":1054114,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"立左都好既<br />\n焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1de0f4c43c706a52506ae53833eba9c368de1e","tid":1054114,"uid":129878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:49:03.00